revival in

00:42:26.359 --> 00:42:29.349
Africa, England,

00:42:29.359 --> 00:42:32.270
Europe,

00:42:32.280 --> 00:42:35.150
Australia,

00:42:35.150 --> 00:42:35.160
and

00:42:35.160 --> 00:42:37.950
Queensland.

00:42:37.960 --> 00:42:41.430
Stir

00:42:41.440 --> 00:42:43.390
the hearts of the preachers

00:42:46.520 --> 00:42:48.230
to

00:42:55.079 --> 00:42:57.270
be bold.

00:43:05.880 --> 00:43:08.910
We praise You

00:43:11.230 --> 00:43:11.240
for

00:43:13.440 --> 00:43:18.150
a new hunger and thirst after

00:43:18.160 --> 00:43:20.109
righteousness.

00:43:27.599 --> 00:43:29.589
We call marriages

00:43:29.599 --> 00:43:31.990
restored and bodies

00:43:33.720 --> 00:43:35.589
healed.

00:43:39.480 --> 00:43:43.349
Thank you for joining me today.

00:43:43.349 --> 00:43:43.359
I

00:43:43.359 --> 00:43:45.910
appreciate

00:43:45.920 --> 00:43:47.950
all the support

00:43:49.880 --> 00:43:52.109
and

00:43:55.119 --> 00:43:57.109
kindness

00:43:57.109 --> 00:43:57.119
during

00:43:57.119 --> 00:43:59.630
this Christmas

00:43:59.640 --> 00:44:03.109
season. Happy Birthday, Jesus!

00:44:03.109 --> 00:44:03.119
He

00:44:03.119 --> 00:44:06.030
is

00:44:06.040 --> 00:44:07.710
my Lord and Savior. We always have

00:44:07.710 --> 00:44:07.720
a cake for

00:44:07.720 --> 00:44:09.589
Him

00:44:09.599 --> 00:44:13.430
as

00:44:13.440 --> 00:44:15.549
a

00:44:18.510 --> 00:44:18.520
family

00:44:20.670 --> 00:44:20.680
and

00:44:23.000 --> 00:44:25.829
sing Happy Birthday.

00:44:30.359 --> 00:44:32.109
Some

00:44:41.960 --> 00:44:44.829
might

00:44:53.760 --> 00:44:55.470
think

00:45:03.599 --> 00:45:05.390
that's silly, but He

00:45:05.400 --> 00:45:09.510
loves it. If you make a place for

00:45:09.520 --> 00:45:13.109
Him in your house, He'll visit

00:45:13.119 --> 00:45:15.630
you.

00:45:15.640 --> 00:45:19.670
Come to Him as a child, not

00:45:19.680 --> 00:45:22.750
an adult.

00:45:53.040 --> 00:45:56.109
He

00:45:58.640 --> 00:46:01.549
is

00:46:03.520 --> 00:46:05.549
the

00:46:08.920 --> 00:46:11.109
Lord

00:46:11.119 --> 00:46:12.309
of

00:46:12.319 --> 00:46:13.750
the

00:46:13.760 --> 00:46:17.549
Harvest,

00:46:17.549 --> 00:46:17.559
and

00:46:17.559 --> 00:46:19.470
all He cares about is

00:46:19.480 --> 00:46:22.150
your heart.

00:46:27.000 --> 00:46:30.510
He died for

00:46:30.510 --> 00:46:30.520
you and

00:46:30.520 --> 00:46:32.790
rose again so you wouldn't

00:46:32.790 --> 00:46:32.800
have to go

00:46:32.800 --> 00:46:37.069
through hell. I've seen

00:46:37.069 --> 00:46:37.079
the holes

00:46:37.079 --> 00:46:38.270
in His hands

00:46:38.270 --> 00:46:38.280
and feet;

00:46:38.280 --> 00:46:41.349
He did

00:46:59.599 --> 00:47:03.390
it all

00:47:03.400 --> 00:47:04.309
for

00:47:04.319 --> 00:47:07.230
you.

00:47:08.599 --> 00:47:12.510
All

00:47:12.520 --> 00:47:15.190
you have to do is receive it by faith.

00:47:21.480 --> 00:47:24.510
Put a smile on your face and a song

00:47:24.520 --> 00:47:27.190
in your heart. Jesus loves you so much,

00:47:27.200 --> 00:47:29.349
and we will see you

00:47:29.359 --> 00:47:32.270
again tomorrow.

00:47:32.280 --> 00:47:35.280
Bye-bye.

